OL,3,CWoman 'searched for husband and son
OL,4,Cfor years' after Omagh bomb
OL,6,FA woman whose husband and son were
OL,7,Fkilled in the Omagh bomb has described
OL,8,Fhow years after the blast she would
OL,9,Fdrive around looking for them,
OL,10,Fbelieving they were still alive.
OL,12,FEdith White said she would also
OL,13,Fregularly change her son Bryan's bed
OL,14,Fsheets, but that he never came home.
OL,16,FBryan, 27, was shopping in Omagh with
OL,17,Fhis father Fred when the bomb exploded.
