OL,3,CWoman 'searched for husband and son
OL,4,Cfor years' after Omagh bomb
OL,6,FIn a statement read out by Hugh
OL,7,FSouthey KC, Edith told the Omagh
OL,8,FBombing Inquiry that the family has
OL,9,Fjust returned home from a holiday when
OL,10,FFred and Bryan went into town.
OL,12,FShe said that not long after they
OL,13,Fleft, she heard a bang.
OL,15,FShe said she has little memory of the
OL,16,Fhours and days after discovering her
OL,17,Fhusband and son had been killed.
