OL,3,CWoman 'searched for husband and son
OL,4,Cfor years' after Omagh bomb
OL,6,FMrs White said: "In the years after
OL,7,Fthe bomb, I just couldn't accept that
OL,8,Fthey were gone. I don't understand why
OL,9,Fthey had to be murdered.
OL,11,F"For a number of years after the bomb,
OL,12,FI would still go in the car to look
OL,13,Ffor them, thinking that they must be
OL,14,Fsomewhere. Whenever I saw a black Ford
OL,15,Fcar, I would have looked to see if
OL,16,Fit's the number plate of Fred's car.
OL,26,@nD@QOUsD@AOU
