OL,3,CWoman 'searched for husband and son
OL,4,Cfor years' after Omagh bomb
OL,6,F"We didn't socialise that much. We
OL,7,Fwent on holidays and just stuck to our
OL,8,Fown activities.
OL,10,F"It wrecks your life, and I think if I
OL,11,Faccept it, then I will just not be
OL,12,Fable to cope. I need to be able to
OL,13,Fblock it out as best I can and say it
OL,14,Fcan't have happened, it's important
OL,15,Fnot to change.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/9
