OL,3,CWoman 'searched for husband and son
OL,4,Cfor years' after Omagh bomb
OL,6,F"But I must say, as time gets on, it
OL,7,Fgets harder to think it hasn't
OL,8,Fhappened. Sometimes the anger builds
OL,9,Fup and I have to cry to myself, but
OL,10,Fthen I try to distract myself by doing
OL,11,Fsomething else."
OL,13,FShe said the years following the bomb,
OL,14,Fthe media reports about public fall-
OL,15,Fouts and the government's response to
OL,16,Fthe incident has added to the pain.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@PO]
