OL,3,CWoman 'searched for husband and son
OL,4,Cfor years' after Omagh bomb
OL,6,F"All the families want to know what
OL,7,Fhappened to their loved ones, but I do
OL,8,Ffeel that how the government has
OL,9,Ftreated us has resulted in a lot of
OL,10,Funnecessary disagreements amongst the
OL,11,Ffamilies," she added.
OL,13,F"I hope this inquiry will help to
OL,14,Funite the families as we all share the
OL,15,Fsame pain and suffering when all our
OL,16,Floved ones were murdered."
OL,18,FA photograph of the pair which was
OL,19,Ftaken the day before the blast shows
OL,20,FFred and Bryan on the last day of
OL,21,Ftheir holiday.
