OL,3,CWoman 'searched for husband and son
OL,4,Cfor years' after Omagh bomb
OL,6,FIn a pre-recorded statement, Fred's
OL,7,Fdaughter Linda said that her mental
OL,8,Fand physical health has been impacted
OL,9,Fby the loss of her father and brother.
OL,11,FShe said she has done things
OL,12,Fdifferently in life as a result of the
OL,13,Fatrocity.
OL,15,F"I think the bomb has forced me to
OL,16,Frelive a lot of trauma and pain and
OL,17,Floss from my past," she added.
OL,19,FLinda read an extract from a poem by
OL,20,FDonna Ashworth about grief.
OL,26,@wD@AOUyD@SO]
